Subject: [PATCH 4/5] Export NewConsensusAPIWithoutHeartbeat, add Close to
 sender cacher

- Export the heartbeat-free ConsensusAPI constructor for testing
- Add Close() to txSenderCacher to stop background goroutines

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
